<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Pending Parcel</title>
    <style type="text/css">
        body{
            margin:0;
            padding: 0;
            min-width:100%;
            font-family: Arial,sans-serif;
            font-size:16px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            background-color: #FAFAFA;
            color:#222222;
        }
        a{
            color:#000;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        h1{
            font-size:24px;
            font-weight:700;
            line-height:1.25;
            margin-top:0;
            margin-bottom:15px;
            text-align:center;
        }
        .status{
            background-color: #1E1E1E;
            color: #fff; 
            width: 70px; 
            padding: 10px;
        }
        p{
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }
        table td{
            vertical-align: top;
        }
        .email-wrapper{
            max-width:700px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        .email-header{
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 30px;
            color: #f2c4ed;
        }

        .email-body{
            padding:14px;
            background-color: #7da6e9;
         
        }
        .email-footer{
            background-color: #e1e5ed;        
            padding: 14px;
        }

        img{
            background-color: #7da6e9;
            padding: 24px; 
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="email-wrapper">

        <div class="email-header">
            <h1>Pending Parcel</h1>
        </div>         
        <div class="email-body">  
        <p>Hello <%= sendername %>,</p>
        <p>You've a parcel that has been sent:</p>
        <p>Here are the details:</p>
        <p>From: <%= from %></p>
        <p>To: <%= to %></p>
        <p>Sender: <%= sendername %></p>
        <p>Recipient: <%= recipientname %></p>
        <p>Cost: $ <%= cost %></p>
        <p>Weight: <%= weight %></p>
        <p>Note: <%= note %></p>
        <p class="status">Pending</p>
        <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dmxvkl3mb/image/upload/v1753156102/image1_i4z1i1.jpg" alt="" height="250px" width="500px">
        <h3>Note:</h3>
        <p>Please if you were not sending or receiving the parcel ignore this email.</p>
        
        </div>
        <div class="email-footer">
            <p>If you have any questions, please don't hesitate to contact us at <a href="mailto:parcelflow74@gmail.com">ParcelFlow@outlook.com</a></a></p>
        </div>
    </div>    
</body>
</html>